room_title: Escape room "“Ghost of Tituba”, the first Salem Witch" by Code To Escape in Daytona Beach
room_address: 119 S Palmetto Ave Daytona Beach, FL 32114
room_description: Didn't anyone tell you to never speak to strangers or dawdle in the forest? The first Salem Witch Tituba lured you into her hut, and now you have to help her brew a mysterious potion. Unless you find all the necessary ingredients in 60 minutes, you will have to serve Tituba for all eternity!
